Samsung Gen 6 Heat Pump with Joule DHW cylinder
FSV Settings
103* – Water Out Temp. for Heat, Max: 43°C, Min: 22°C
104* – Room Temp. for Heat, Max: 24°C, Min: 16°C
201* – Outdoor Temp. for Water Law (Heat), Low: 14°C, High: -2°C
175sqm, Detatched 4 bedroom house, A1 rated. 
3 zones - Underfloor, Downstairs Radiators, Upstairs Radiators
Maximise use of heat pump during low cost period, use underfloor zone as heat battery, ensure comfort at lowest cost (even at the expense of COP)
Tariff: day/night rates €0.33 / €0.08.
Heating during DHW detected: zone pumps active during DHW can cause return mixing and low COP; attribute DHW efficiency penalties accordingly.
